<h1>Blockade Navigation Prerequisites</h1>
<p style="font-style:italic">Note that this article is subject to change.</p>
<p>This series of Blockade Navigation articles gives you a brief introduction to some of the knowledge and skills that you will need as a Blockade Navigator.  In this article, I will describe what these skills are, and what they are not.</p>
<p>These articles are about Blockades specifically, they assume that you understand how to manage a large ship and how to engage in a PvP battle.  The articles will explain some of the core concepts that make Blockading different to a voyage or a PvP battle, so it is important that you understand these concepts in order to understand the ones put forward in these articles.</p>

